column1: Supplementary Table 1.  List of mitochondrial SNPs on the custom panel associated with Hi-MC.  For each SNP, the mito SNP ID, rs number (if avaialble), classifying allele, associated haplogroup, and references to the haplogrouping assignments (in PubMed IDs) are given.  Note that the associated haplogroup shown is based on the reduced PhyloTree presented in Mitchell et al 2014 (PMID:24488180 and PMC4113317).  Also, the haplogroup in the associated haplogroup column may require other SNPs in the custom panel for this assignment.  Please referece to Mitchell et al 2014 for details.
